programRules.condition:
(d2:hasValue('HEIGHT') && d2:zScoreHFA(d2:monthsBetween(A{DOB}, V{event_date}), #{HEIGHT}, A{SEX}) >= -2 &&

((d2:hasValue('WEIGHT') && d2:zScoreWFA(d2:monthsBetween(A{DOB}, V{event_date}), #{WEIGHT}, A{SEX}) >= -2) &&
(d2:zScoreWFA(d2:monthsBetween(A{DOB}, V{event_date}), #{WEIGHT}, A{SEX}) < 2)) &&

(d2:hasValue('HB_HEMOCUE') && #{HB_HEMOCUE} >= 110))
